This create segfault in arm64 audio plugins when built with optimisations on.

```d
    package uint arm_get_fpcr() pure nothrow @nogc @trusted
    {
        return __asm!uint("mrs $0, fpcr", "=r");
    }

    package void arm_set_fpcr(uint cw) nothrow @nogc @trusted
    {
        __asm!void("ldr w2, $0 \n msr fpcr, x2", "m", cw);
    }
```

When inlined, this will erase the content of good register. Find a way to either mark the register as dirtied, or replace with LDC_intrinsic.

